Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.75,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}脱了我就知道了啦
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.63,0:13:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服哦
